# Files copied into every new git worktree Claude Code creates.
#
# A worktree is a fresh checkout, so gitignored files do not exist in it. Without
# this list a worktree would have no .env, and every script here would fail with
# "DEEPSEEK_API_KEY not found" -- which looks like a broken key rather than a
# missing file.
#
# Uses .gitignore syntax. Only files that match AND are gitignored are copied,
# so tracked files are never duplicated.
#
# Note: this does put the API key in each worktree directory. They live under
# .claude/worktrees/ which is gitignored, so it never reaches the remote.
.env
